{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HhjbXQZKLq5U4ncziTaG7k","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tid: SLICE-0072\n3\taliases:\n4\t  - SLICE-0072\n5\ttitle: Generate per-project index.md at wiki sync\n6\tproject: wiki-v2\n7\tstatus: planned\n8\ttype: AFK\n9\tblocked_by: []\n10\tuser_stories: []\n11\tacceptance:\n12\t  - wiki sync --project p writes projects/p/index.md\n13\t  - >-\n14\t    index.md lists every artifact with linked id, title, summary, status read\n15\t    from frontmatter (no prose duplication)\n16\t  - >-\n17\t    Re-running sync is idempotent: same vault state produces byte-identical\n18\t    index.md\n19\t  - wiki create does NOT write or touch index.md (create stays pure)\n20\ttdd_exempt: false\n21\trelated: []\n22\tcreated: '2026-06-23'\n23\tupdated: '2026-06-23'\n24\t---\n25\t# Generate per-project index.md at wiki sync\n26\t\n27\t> SLICE-0072 · wiki-v2 · `INPUT[select(option(planned), option(red), option(green), option(closed), option(blocked), option(superseded)):status]` · `INPUT[select(option(AFK), option(HITL)):type]`\n28\t\n29\t## Parent\n30\t\n31\t[[]]\n32\t\n33\t## What to build\n34\t\n35\tImplements [[ADR-0036]] #2. In `src/cli/verbs/sync.ts`, after the qmd embed loop, scan every artifact under `projects/<project>/`, read frontmatter (id, title, summary, status, group), and write `projects/<project>/index.md` — a plain markdown table/list that renders in CLI, GitHub, and Obsidian (no Dataview/Bases). Sort by kind then id. Overwrite on every sync; idempotent. Sectioning by `group:` comes from the group slice — until then, one flat list. Per-project granularity only (no per-kind sub-index). Never written by create.\n36\t\n37\t## Acceptance criteria\n38\t\n39\t- [ ] wiki sync --project p writes projects/p/index.md\n40\t- [ ] index.md lists every artifact with linked id, title, summary, status read from frontmatter (no prose duplication)\n41\t- [ ] Re-running sync is idempotent: same vault state produces byte-identical index.md\n42\t- [ ] wiki create does NOT write or touch index.md (create stays pure)\n43\t\n44\t\n45\t## Todo\n46\t\n47\t- [ ] Write tests\n48\t- [ ] Implement feature\n49\t- [ ] Verify acceptance criteria\n50\t\n51\t> Slice close (`wiki slice close`) is gated on every item above being done.\n52\t\n53\t## Blocked by\n54\t\n55\tNone — can start immediately.\n56\t\n57\t\n58\t## Evidence\n59\t\n60\t- **Red log:** \n61\t- **Green log:** \n62\t- **Review verdict:** \n63\t\n64\t> Set automatically by the slice state machine. See ADR-0005.\n65\t\n66\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"28ab8cbe-87eb-42f8-8aa3-f40cdb29823c","uuid":"8ed429c9-6d45-4a92-82aa-56a8d0090f2a","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:38:57.188Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/tothemoon/Knowledge/projects/wiki-v2/slices/SLICE-0072-generate-per-project-index-md-at-wiki-sync.md","content":"---\nid: SLICE-0072\naliases:\n  - SLICE-0072\ntitle: Generate per-project index.md at wiki sync\nproject: wiki-v2\nstatus: planned\ntype: AFK\nblocked_by: []\nuser_stories: []\nacceptance:\n  - wiki sync --project p writes projects/p/index.md\n  - >-\n    index.md lists every artifact with linked id, title, summary, status read\n    from frontmatter (no prose duplication)\n  - >-\n    Re-running sync is idempotent: same vault state produces byte-identical\n    index.md\n  - wiki create does NOT write or touch index.md (create stays pure)\ntdd_exempt: false\nrelated: []\ncreated: '2026-06-23'\nupdated: '2026-06-23'\n---\n# Generate per-project index.md at wiki sync\n\n> SLICE-0072 · wiki-v2 · `INPUT[select(option(planned), option(red), option(green), option(closed), option(blocked), option(superseded)):status]` · `INPUT[select(option(AFK), option(HITL)):type]`\n\n## Parent\n\n[[]]\n\n## What to build\n\nImplements [[ADR-0036]] #2. In `src/cli/verbs/sync.ts`, after the qmd embed loop, scan every artifact under `projects/<project>/`, read frontmatter (id, title, summary, status, group), and write `projects/<project>/index.md` — a plain markdown table/list that renders in CLI, GitHub, and Obsidian (no Dataview/Bases). Sort by kind then id. Overwrite on every sync; idempotent. Sectioning by `group:` comes from the group slice — until then, one flat list. Per-project granularity only (no per-kind sub-index). Never written by create.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- [ ] wiki sync --project p writes projects/p/index.md\n- [ ] index.md lists every artifact with linked id, title, summary, status read from frontmatter (no prose duplication)\n- [ ] Re-running sync is idempotent: same vault state produces byte-identical index.md\n- [ ] wiki create does NOT write or touch index.md (create stays pure)\n\n\n## Todo\n\n- [ ] Write tests\n- [ ] Implement feature\n- [ ] Verify acceptance criteria\n\n> Slice close (`wiki slice close`) is gated on every item above being done.\n\n## Blocked by\n\nNone — can start immediately.\n\n\n## Evidence\n\n- **Red log:** \n- **Green log:** \n- **Review verdict:** \n\n> Set automatically by the slice state machine. See ADR-0005.\n\n","numLines":66,"startLine":1,"totalLines":66}}}
